name: Hungry Clicker Style Lora
description:
Hungry Clicker Style

Trained by aziib

weight recommended: 0.6 or 0.7

This model is mimicking hungry clicker art style like brushy painting texture and some thick line. it's recomend use negative prompt or negative embedding to get better result. also if you want to generate male character, make sure you type female at negative prompt so it will generate male character instead of female. no need to add gender negative prompt anymore on version 2

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description: added more datasets and better for detecting male or female gender
